ty Media\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"https://frosty.media\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"width\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"32\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"height\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"32\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:4:\"item\";a:6:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Style Pack #2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 10 Mar 2015 21:18:01 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=37571\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:312:\"<p>Custom Login Style Pack #2. Easily activate four different WordPress login styles at the click of a button.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/\">Style Pack #2</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6817:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>Have you wanted to add that extra touch to your WordPress login page? Have you been looking for ways to customize every part of your site to your personal or business brand? </p>\n<p>My guess is you&#8217;ve answered yes to one of those questions. With <a href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login 3.0\">Custom Login</a> it&#8217;s easy to brand your login page with the change of a few settings.</p>\n<h3>Adding Custom Style</h3>\n<p>What this style pack offers is four customized settings that you could activate at the click of a button. Upon activation you can do nothing and enjoy the new custom login style or tinker with the settings by adding your own logo or additional CSS, HTML or jQuery.</p>\n<h4>#1 The <em>Car Enthusiast</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-1024x797.png\" alt=\"Custom Login Car Enthusiast\" width=\"1024\" height=\"797\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-37576\" srcset=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-1024x797.png 1024w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-300x233.png 300w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-643x500.png 643w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset.png 1189w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><br />\n<em>This style is for the car enthusiast, the background is a 2015 WRX on the beach. The form will slide down with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#2 The <em>Winter Wonderland</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-1024x797.png\" alt=\"Custom Login Snow\" width=\"1024\" height=\"797\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-37578\" srcset=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-1024x797.png 1024w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-300x233.png 300w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-643x500.png 643w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn.png 1189w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack has that fresh snow ovcast feeling. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#3 The <em>Squirrel</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-1024x768.png\" alt=\"Custom Login Squirrel Tree\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-37579\" srcset=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-1024x768.png 1024w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-300x225.png 300w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-175x131.png 175w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-666x500.png 666w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree.png 1233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is has fun written all over it, bright green with a squirrel looking right at you. The form will flip in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#4 The <em>Dutch Vacation</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-1024x768.png\" alt=\"Custom Login Dutch Aruba\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-37580\" srcset=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-1024x768.png 1024w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-300x225.png 300w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-175x131.png 175w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-666x500.png 666w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up.png 1233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack has that dark secretive vibe. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h3>How-to install</h3>\n<p>Follow this <a href=\"//frosty.media/docs/installing-custom-login-extensions/\">documentation</a> guide.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-wrx-sunset/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-login-snow-no-turn/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-squirrel-tree/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-dutch-fade-up/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-fade-up-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-snow-fade-down/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-snow-fade-down-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-squirrel-flip-in/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-flip-in-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-wrx-fade-down/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-fade-down-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/\">Style Pack #2</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Style Pack #1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 02 Feb 2015 19:06:34 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=25584\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:358:\"<p>Use the coupon code \"CustomLogin500K\" and download Custom Login Style Pack #1 for free, a $10 value. Custom Login Style Pack is a Custom Login Extension.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/\">Style Pack #1</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5754:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>Have you wanted to add that extra touch to your WordPress login page? Have you been looking for ways to customize every part of your site to your personal or business brand? </p>\n<p>My guess is you&#8217;ve answered yes to one of those questions. With <a href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login 3.0\">Custom Login</a> it&#8217;s easy to brand your login page with the change of a few settings.</p>\n<h3>Adding Custom Style</h3>\n<p>What this style pack offers is four customized settings that you could activate at the click of a button. Upon activation you can do nothing and enjoy the new custom login style or tinker with the settings by adding your own logo or additional CSS, HTML or jQuery.</p>\n<h4>#1 The <em>Light Blue Slide In</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-light-blue-slide-in.gif\" alt=\"Light Blue Style Pack w/ Slide in CSS3 animation\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25968\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is light but packs a blue punch. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#2 The <em>Jagged Zoom Right In</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-jagged-zoom-right-in.gif\" alt=\"Jagged Rock Style Pack w/ Zoom right in CSS3 animation\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25976\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is has soft earth colors but has that sharpe jagged edge. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#3 The <em>Wood Fade In Down</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-wood-fade-in-down.gif\" alt=\"Wood Style Pack w/ Fade in Down CSS3 animation\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25969\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is rich with a dynamic wood background. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#4 The <em>Fog Fade In Up</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-fog-fade-in-up.gif\" alt=\"Fog Style Pack w/ Fade in up CSS3 animation\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25966\" /><br />\n<em>This style pack has that dark secretive vibe. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h3>How-to install</h3>\n<p>Follow this <a href=\"//frosty.media/docs/installing-custom-login-extensions/\">documentation</a> guide.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-gray-fog/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-gray-fog-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-jagged-rock/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-jagged-rock-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-light-blue/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-light-blue-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-style-pack-settings-1/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-style-pack-settings-1-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-style-pack-settings-2/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-style-pack-settings-2-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-wood/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-wood-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-fog-fade-in-up/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-fog-fade-in-up-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Fog Style Pack w/ Fade in up CSS3 animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-light-blue-slide-in/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-light-blue-slide-in-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Light Blue Style Pack w/ Slide in CSS3 animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-wood-fade-in-down/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-wood-fade-in-down-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Wood Style Pack w/ Fade in Down CSS3 animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-jagged-zoom-right-in/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-jagged-zoom-right-in-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Jagged Rock Style Pack w/ Zoom right in CSS3 animation\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/\">Style Pack #1</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"No Password Login\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 06 Oct 2014 03:35:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=129\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:326:\"<p>Login Without Password in WordPress? Now you can with this Custom Login extension: No Password Login WordPress. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\">No Password Login</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1761:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>Allow users to login without having to remember their password. This plugin is safe and secure and uses WordPress&#8217; best coding practices.</p>\n<p>With a simple shortcode you can allow a form where a user can enter their email or username which then sends them an email with a login URL key. That URL can only be used once and expires after 10 min.</p>\n<h3>An example</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/custom-login-no-password-login.gif\" alt=\"Custom Login No Password Login animation\" width=\"1190\" height=\"765\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16624\" /></p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/custom-login-no-password-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/custom-login-no-password-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login No Password settings\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/custom-login-no-password-login-2/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/custom-login-no-password-login-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login No Password Login animation\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\">No Password Login</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Login Redirects\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 25 Apr 2014 03:31:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=125\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:325:\"<p>Manage user roles and redirect said user after successful logins with this Custom Login Redirect extension for WordPress.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\">Login Redirects</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3542:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>When it comes to managing a WordPress site which allows signups, you rarely want subscriber roles to view the dashboard or admin pages after they log in.</p>\n<h3>WordPress solutions</h3>\n<p>WordPress has many hooks and filters which allow you to control visibility access on a user role base. But this method requires you to understand PHP.</p>\n<p>So, here’s an easy way to redirect subscribers users (or which ever role you&#8217;d like) to a default WordPress page or custom URL (of your choosing) after said user logs in.</p>\n<h3>How to use it</h3>\n<p>There is really only four options needed for this plugin, and three of those have default values. </p>\n<ol>\n<li>On/Off</li>\n<li><del datetime=\"2014-11-04T00:53:21+00:00\">Redirect minimum user role.</del> <ins datetime=\"2014-11-04T00:53:21+00:00\">Removed in 1.1.0</ins></li>\n<li>Redirect To (A WordPress page).</li>\n<li>Redirect URL (when Redirect to equals &#8220;A Custom URL&#8221;) <em>local URLs only</em>.</li>\n<li>Redirect to URL for each registered role (if empty uses the <em>Redirect URL</em> setting).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Manage user roles and redirect said user after successful logins with this Custom Login Redirect extension for WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings-150x150.png 150w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings-300x300.png 300w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings-1024x1021.png 1024w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings-501x500.png 501w, https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings.png 1180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-custom-url/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-custom-url-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects custom URL redirect animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-wp-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-wp-page-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects WordPress page URL redirect animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-user-roles/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-user-roles-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects redirect URL by user role animation\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\">Login Redirects</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Page Template\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 29 Jan 2014 04:24:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=121\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:343:\"<p>The Custom Login Page Template is an extension for the Custom Login WordPress plugin allowing login forms to be generated on any WP page.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/\">Page Template</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2282:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>Create your own WordPress Custom Login page from any page you previously created in WordPress.</p>\n<p class=\"alert\">You must <a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Codex:Creating_a_New_Page\" target=\"_blank\">create</a> a new blank WordPress page or use an existing one. Note: the content will be replaced with the login form.</p>\n<h3>How to use it</h3>\n<p>There is only two options in this plugin, and one turns it on and off.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>On/Off</li>\n<li>Your custom login page.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! Once setup the WordPress login form will replace the default content on the page set in the settings.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/custom-login-page-template-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/custom-login-page-template-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/custom-login-page-template-setting-enabled/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/custom-login-page-template-setting-enabled-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/custom-login-page-template-login-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/custom-login-page-template-login-page-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/page-template-login-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/page-template-login-page-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/\">Page Template</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Stealth Login\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 17 Apr 2013 02:44:12 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=109\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:344:\"<p>Custom Login Stealth Login protects your wp-login.php page from brute force attacks by requiring a authentication key and code in the URL.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/\">Stealth Login</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3482:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>By now you seen all the stories of WordPress sites being vulnerable to brute force attacks. But what does it really mean? Simply put, a hacker or generated computer program is targeting your <code>wp-login.php</code> page and is trying to log in hundreds (if not thousands) of times with the most generic usernames and random &#8220;popular&#8221; passwords.</p>\n<p>One step is to change your <a href=\"http://torquemag.io/goodbye-admin-user/\">admin</a> username. But that still leaves your site open to thousands of login attempts. You can use a login IP limiter, but a hacker can use many IPs or proxy their IP and your website will likely crash before all IPs are blocked. <strong>I know, because this happened to me</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Is there a simple solution?</h3>\n<p>How about <em>hiding</em> the <code>wp-login.php</code> page&#8230;</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s exactingly what Custom Login Stealth Login is intended for. It gives you one solution <strong>with</strong> two options for unauthorized users.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Redirects</strong>: If a user doesn&#8217;t have the correct &#8220;key&#8221; and &#8220;code&#8221;, redirect them away from the page.</li>\n<li><strong>Die</strong>: <em>This is a programming term</em> If a user doesn&#8217;t have the correct &#8220;key&#8221; and &#8220;code&#8221;, kill the generation of the page with a displayed message.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>How to use it</h3>\n<p>There is really on five options needed for this plugin, and three of those have default values. </p>\n<ol>\n<li>On/Off</li>\n<li>Redirect(On)/Kill the page(Off)</li>\n<li>Redirect URL (when Redirect is &#8220;On&#8221;)</li>\n<li>Question (the query variable or &#8220;<strong>key</strong>&#8220;)</li>\n<li>Answer (The query answer or &#8220;<strong>code</strong>&#8220;)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Simple! Once setup your login page can <strong>only</strong> be accessed by visiting <code>yourwebsite.com/wp-login.php?question=answer</code> <strong>where</strong> <em>question</em> is the <strong>question</strong> you set and <em>answer</em> is the <strong>answer</strong> you set in the settings. These settings are defaulted to <code>bypass=true</code>.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/custom-login-stealth-login-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/custom-login-stealth-login-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/stealth-login-kill-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/stealth-login-kill-page-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/stealth-login-redirect/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/stealth-login-redirect-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/\">Stealth Login</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:77:\"https://frosty.media/feed/?post_type=plugin&plugin_tag=custom-login-extension\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:11:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Tue, 26 Sep 2017 20:28:09 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:7:\"expires\";s:29:\"Thu, 19 Nov 1981 08:52:00 GMT\";s:13:\"cach